    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior is clean with only minor surface scratches and small rock chips consistent with regular use, while the interior remains comfortable and free of major stains or tears. Mechanically, the car runs smoothly, the engine sounds strong, and all major electronics are fully functional. This is a reliable daily driver that offers a great balance of performance and value for its next owner.",
