    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained, making it a reliable choice for its next owner. The exterior remains clean with a nice finish, though you may notice a few minor surface scratches and small stone chips consistent with regular use. Inside, the cabin is well-preserved and comfortable, showing only light wear on the driver's seat bolster and primary touchpoints. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and has a documented service history, ensuring it is ready for the road with no immediate repairs needed.",
